          "candidate_value": "Over 2,150 BMO ATM in Canada means that there are plenty of convenient places to bank on the go Enjoy unlimited non- BMO ATM withdrawals worldwide *53 with the Premium Plan Chequing Account Take advantage of online services like Interac e-Transfer \u00ae\u2021 footnote registered section t",
